---
layout: base.njk
title: Page not found
description: The page could not be found. Browse the latest engineering log entries, tags, or the Atom feed.
keywords: 404, not found, engineering log, tags, Atom feed
permalink: /404.html
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<section>
  <h1>Page not found</h1>
  <p class="intro">That URL does not exist here. Start from the latest entries, browse tags, or use the feed.</p>
  <ul class="log-list">
    <li><a href="/">Latest entries</a></li>
    <li><a href="/tags/">Browse tags</a></li>
    <li><a href="/feed.xml">Atom feed</a></li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Recent entries</h2>
  <ul class="log-list">
    {% for entry in collections.entries %}
      {% if loop.index <= 5 %}
        <li>
          <time datetime="{{ entry.date | isoDate }}">{{ entry.date | readableDate }}</time>
          <a href="{{ entry.url }}">{{ entry.data.title }}</a>
        </li>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>